                     <interp inst="t18430612-1796-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18430612-cd-66" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430612-1796-offence-1 t18430612-cd-66"></join>12th of June</rs>, 631bs. weight of lead, value 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18430612-name-559" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-559" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
